					<li>ðŸ‘‰ Background email processing using Laravel Jobs.</li>
					<li>ðŸ‘‰ Foreground and background data imports using Laravel Commands.</li>
					<li>ðŸ‘‰ Administration panel with Nova 3.0, utilizing Actions, Metrics, Tools, and Resource Tools.</li>
					<li>ðŸ‘‰ Integration of React to implement a custom admin panel.</li>
					<li>ðŸ‘‰ Development of endpoints for exporting data in multiple formats (CSV, JSON, Excel).</li>
					<li>ðŸ‘‰ Enhancements to the existing checkout system.</li>
					<li>ðŸ‘‰ Creation of new Models, Migrations, Controllers, and Observers.</li>
					<li>ðŸ‘‰ Improvements to the existing promotions system.</li>
